IN RE: BAR ADMISSIONS CFN-296758 NO. 2018-BA-0417 Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 16, 2018

Motion to file untimely petition denied. Petition for admission to the bar not considered. Supreme Court Rule XVII, § 9(B). Pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 9(D)(13), petitioner may not seek admission until one year after October 6, 2017.

JOHNSON, C.J., would grant and consider the petition.

HUGHES, J., would grant and consider the petition.
